{"tid":2211133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"焦土派的問題","createTime":"2020-09-21T02:37:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T14:59:48.000Z","uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d6986c528874efca277a7bc9bf5cb132788981","tid":2211133,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T02:37:12.000Z","msg":"小弟自從上年開始已經係焦土派嘅信徒<br />\n咁其實焦土代表要摧毁一個地方再重新建立<br />\n因為我覺得香港舊有嘅制度其實都係有問題<br />\n但獨派理論我都會接受 不過冇分要文化建國定種族建國  唯一信奉嘅就係武力建國<br />\n咁樣又算唔算好純粹嘅焦土信徒？<br />\n<br />\n另外我想知有乜嘢代表性嘅人物？<br />\n唔好同我講攬炒巴"},{"pid":"458664af32bac10ef38437aee546996621a65cf8","tid":2211133,"uid":24814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"焦土嘅定義係毀壞地面上所有的一切 包含農作物 工廠和城市 破壞任何可能對敵人有用的東西<br />\n但香港焦土派唔係 係要益哂對家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beac1300be9837628b6c296ad1eb79f2e052af81","tid":2211133,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"「焦土派」不是一個派別<br />\n（焦土 只是 策略）<br />\n<br />\n建制派<br />\n民主派<br />\n本土派<br />\n<br />\n以上才是 派別"},{"pid":"a3dfedf4be986df414b68195e6bc5c22d2cf90ad","tid":2211133,"uid":346260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T05:57:47.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"medium\">大家要小心網絡安全，尤其是<ins>被咬過嘅手足</ins>，電話可能已經<span class=\"red\">被入侵</span>。港共可以用<span class=\"gold\">stingray</span><strong><span class=\"violet\">大規模監控</span></strong>某個<span class=\"limegreen\">大範圍</span>嘅<strong><span class=\"pink\">所有電話</span></strong>，<span class=\"red\">偷取IMSI(夠識別所有人)</span>，甚至<span class=\"violet\">截取通訊</span>。<strong>好多手足就係唔注重私隱同網絡安全<span class=\"red\">被咬</span></strong>，好大機會包括<strong><span class=\"limegreen\">被綁架12人</span></strong>; 記得追蹤基爾巴: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/96327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/96327</a><br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><ins><strong>請簽署制裁綁架12人嘅支那官員:<span class=\"x-small\"><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZopE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=e6aa4b52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-chinese-officials-culpable-wrongfully-detaining-12-hong-kong-citizens-and-denying-their-right-counsel</a><br />\n</span></ins></strong></span>[實用文] 教您點先可以保障私隱、網絡安全 (簡易版)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2194107</a><br />\n樓主可唔可以pin?唔該晒<img src=\"https://cdn.lihkg.com/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fmouse%2Fplease.gif&h=3d3ddc66&s={SIZE}\" /></span>"},{"pid":"88904823dad1e9c939b3035645240d67b0449c2c","tid":2211133,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"beac1300be9837628b6c296ad1eb79f2e052af81","tid":2211133,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"「焦土派」不是一個派別<br />\n（焦土 只是 策略）<br />\n<br />\n建制派<br />\n民主派<br />\n本土派<br />\n<br />\n以上才是 派別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"焦土係一個願景係一目標<br />\n係一個志向"},{"pid":"05bf1ee977b45306078fa8eca1279fe43d435d41","tid":2211133,"uid":370186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"458664af32bac10ef38437aee546996621a65cf8","tid":2211133,"uid":24814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T03:42:54.000Z","msg":"焦土嘅定義係毀壞地面上所有的一切 包含農作物 工廠和城市 破壞任何可能對敵人有用的東西<br />\n但香港焦土派唔係 係要益哂對家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T14:32:11.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n根本仲未肯真正焦土<br />\n根本仲未放得低<br />\n但係其實有邊個係代